    "hc_tab_content_odor_jgnedL": {
      "type": "hc-tab-content-odor",
      "blocks": {
        "types_of_odor_CtjmdV": {
          "type": "types-of-odor",
          "settings": {
            "main_title": "<p>Even the best alternatives can handle only <strong>1 out of 5</strong> types of Odor.<br/>HercLeón Can handle <em>all five.</em></p>",
            "competitor_label": "Silver-infused, Merino Wool, Anti-bacterial, etc.",
            "odor_1_name": "Bacteria",
            "competitor_odor_1_status": "Covered",
            "hercleon_odor_1_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_2_name": "Fungus",
            "competitor_odor_2_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_2_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_3_name": "Body Oils",
            "competitor_odor_3_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_3_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_4_name": "Environment",
            "competitor_odor_4_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_4_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_5_name": "Hormones",
            "competitor_odor_5_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_5_status": "Neutralized",
            "hercleon_label": "HERCLÉON",
            "bottom_content": "<p>Here’s the truth: even the best merino wool or silver-infused shirts only neutralize one of the five types of odor - bacteria. That’s why they still end up smelling 'lived in' after a few wears.<br/><br/>Odor doesn’t come from just one place. It’s a combination of five different sources: bacteria, fungus, body oils, environmental odors (like smoke, food, and pollution), and hormonal sweat triggered by stress or exertion.<br/><br/>We’re the first to create clothing designed to handle all five, so freshness lasts longer and nothing gradually builds up over time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "speak_3MAJHn": {
          "type": "speak",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow_text": "03 — YOUR PRESENCE, UNDISTORTED",
            "title": "Speak For Yourself",
            "content": "<p>Research shows that scent plays a powerful role in first impressions. Our bodies release different odors depending on how we feel, including subtle scent changes linked to stress, anxiety, and pressure. People may not consciously notice it, but they still feel it. And what they feel becomes your “vibe.”<br/><br/>By blocking odor that's triggered by stress, our clothing keeps unwanted signals out of the way. Whether it's a first date, a job interview, a business meeting, or any moment that matters, smell won't give you away before you even speak. HercLéon gives you the freedom to choose your first impression, instead of letting odor choose it for you.</p>",
            "sense_1_label": "Sight (How you look)",
            "sense_1_time": "~0.5s",
            "sense_2_label": "Sound (What you say)",
            "sense_2_time": "~0.7s",
            "sense_3_label": "Scent (Your smell)",
            "sense_3_time": "~0.1s (Instant)",
            "sense_3_note": "Direct connection. No logic filter. Instant emotional judgment."
          }
        },
        "bacteria_anTzAa": {
          "type": "bacteria",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow_text": "01 — ANTI-MICROBIAL DEFENSE",
            "title": "Stop Bacteria. Stop Odor.",
            "content": "<p>One of the main reasons odor becomes noticeable is simple: bacteria naturally present on your skin and clothing have time to break down sweat and body oils, producing odor compounds. Most fabrics don’t inhibit bacteria — they give it time to multiply until smell forms.<br/><br/>HercLéon interrupts that process with mineral-infused HercFiber™. Copper and silver help limit bacterial growth, while zinc and volcanic ash help manage moisture, reducing the conditions bacteria need to thrive. By reducing bacterial buildup early, HercFiber helps stop the odor cycle before it can begin.</p>",
            "material_1_name": "Polyester",
            "material_1_mechanism": "No antibacterial abilities",
            "material_1_reduction": "0%",
            "material_1_speed": "☆☆☆☆☆",
            "material_1_highlight_speed": false,
            "material_2_name": "Cotton",
            "material_2_mechanism": "Minimize moisture availability",
            "material_2_reduction": "5%",
            "material_2_speed": "★☆☆☆☆",
            "material_2_highlight_speed": false,
            "material_3_name": "Merino Wool",
            "material_3_mechanism": "Resists but doesn't kill",
            "material_3_reduction": "30%",
            "material_3_speed": "★☆☆☆☆",
            "material_3_highlight_speed": true,
            "material_4_name": "Silver-Infused",
            "material_4_mechanism": "Ions kill on contact",
            "material_4_reduction": "99.9%",
            "material_4_speed": "★★★☆☆",
            "material_4_highlight_speed": true,
            "material_5_name": "HercFiber™",
            "material_5_mechanism": "Multi-mineral matrix",
            "material_5_reduction": "99.9%",
            "material_5_speed": "★★★★★",
            "footer_text": "HercFiber Works 10-100x Faster Than Silver-Infused Clothing"
          }
        },
        "moisture_control_wfJDJ9": {
          "type": "moisture-control",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow_text": "02 — HYPER-ABSORBENCY",
            "title": "MOISTURE CONTROL",
            "description": "HercFiber is built with a hyper-absorbent fiber system that pulls moisture away instantly, keeping your skin dry. Its ultra-fine structure, thanks to our fibers that are engineered at just 10 microns, creates less friction, traps less heat, and keeps your skin cooler and drier throughout the day. Removing the moist environment bacteria need to grow, odor never gets a chance to form.",
            "card_title": "Skin Moisture Level",
            "card_subtitle": "Bacteria Requires Moisture To Breed",
            "bar_left_label": "Others",
            "bar_right_legend": "Dry",
            "bar_right_label": "HercFiber"
          }
        }
      },
