    "hc_tab_content_briefing_kgWRXP": {
      "type": "hc-tab-content-briefing",
      "blocks": {
        "types_of_odor_BcaRmr": {
          "type": "types-of-odor",
          "settings": {
            "main_title": "<p>Even the best alternatives can handle only <strong>1 out of 5</strong> types of Odor.<br/>HercLeón Can handle <strong>all five.</strong></p>",
            "competitor_label": "Silver-infused, Merino Wool, Anti-bacterial, etc.",
            "odor_1_name": "Bacteria",
            "competitor_odor_1_status": "Covered",
            "hercleon_odor_1_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_2_name": "Fungus",
            "competitor_odor_2_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_2_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_3_name": "Body Oils",
            "competitor_odor_3_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_3_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_4_name": "Environment",
            "competitor_odor_4_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_4_status": "Neutralized",
            "odor_5_name": "Hormones",
            "competitor_odor_5_status": "Ignored",
            "hercleon_odor_5_status": "Neutralized",
            "hercleon_label": "HercLeon",
            "bottom_content": "<p>Here’s the truth: even the best merino wool or silver-infused shirts only neutralize one of the five types of body odor. That’s why they still end up smelling “lived in” after a long day, a stressful moment, or a second wear.<br/><br/>We’re the first to create clothing that handles all five types of odor — so nothing breaks through.<br/><br/>And this matters because smell is one of the oldest senses in the human brain. It bypasses logic and hits emotion instantly. Once your clothes smell, it doesn’t matter how soft they feel or how good they look — you simply can’t wear them.<br/><br/>To make things even trickier, women can smell up to 10× better than men.<br/>So even when you think your merino wool shirt smells fine, it probably doesn’t to most women.<br/><br/>With clothing that neutralizes all five odors, you move through life with quiet confidence — knowing your clothes aren’t betraying you when it matters most.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "travel_pack_kWRLtn": {
          "type": "travel-pack",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Pack lighter. Move freer.",
            "description": "Smell is what forces travelers to overpack — backup shirts, extra socks, spare underwear, \"just in case\" outfits. When your clothes stay fresh day after day, all of that disappears. One HercShirt can replace an entire stack of regular shirts, and our socks and underwear stay clean far beyond a single wear. With HercLeón, you pack lighter, carry less, and move through the world with real freedom.",
            "trip_title": "2 Weeks Long Trip",
            "standard_label": "Standard Tourist",
            "standard_weight": "~3.5kg Load",
            "standard_items": "14",
            "standard_caption": "Requires 14 items OR Laundry",
            "hercleon_label": "HercLeon Operative",
            "hercleon_weight": "~0.1kg Load",
            "hercleon_items": "1",
            "hercleon_caption": "Requires 1 Item. Zero Laundry."
