        "speak_wDqjBL": {
          "type": "speak",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Speak For Yourself",
            "content": "<p>Recent research shows that smell shapes first impressions instantly. It's the only sense that bypasses your logical mind and goes straight into emotion and memory. People don't think about how you smell — they feel it. And what they feel becomes your \"vibe.\"</p><p>That's why we engineered HercLeón to support you in the moments that matter most. Whether it's a first date, a business meeting, or simply stepping out into the world, our smell-proof clothing keeps odor out of the way so your presence comes through clearly.</p><p>You show up confident.<br/>You show up intentional.<br/>You show up unmistakably you.</p><p>HercLeón gives you the freedom to choose your first impression — instead of letting odor choose it for you.</p>",
            "sense_1_label": "Sight (How you look)",
            "sense_1_time": "~0.5s",
            "sense_2_label": "Sound (What you say)",
            "sense_2_time": "~0.7s",
            "sense_3_label": "Scent (Your smell)",
            "sense_3_time": "~0.1s (Instant)",
            "sense_3_note": "Direct connection. No logic filter. Instant emotional judgment."
          }
        },
