        "bacteria_ahQEWC": {
          "type": "bacteria",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Stop Bacteria. Stop Odor.",
            "content": "<p>Odor only exists because bacteria linger long enough to break down sweat. Most fabrics give them hours of freedom — and those hours are all bacteria need to create smell. HercLeón solves this at the source with advanced antibacterial fibers that neutralize bacteria the moment they touch the fabric.</p><p>By removing bacteria up to 100x faster than even the most powerful silver treated clothing our HercFiber stops the entire odor cycle before it can begin. The result is simple: you stay fresher, cleaner, and more confident for far longer.</p><p>Freshness isn't luck — it's engineering.<br/>And it starts with killing bacteria fast.</p>",
